title: Rustic Roasted Eggplant, Bacon & Veggie Risotto with Parmesan Cheese & Chargrilled Capsicum Relish
description: Eggplant and carrot, roasted to golden perfection, are tossed through a herby bacon risotto. You’ll notice the sharp
Parmesan coming through and the chargrilled capsicum relish really elevates this dinner to the next level. Finish it
off with toasty almonds for a nutty a flavour.
